# Licence branch: the DB and source parquets are NOT redistributed. The DB is
# generated client-side from data.gouv.fr (build.js) and persisted in OPFS, or
# downloaded from a deployment URL (config.js). A pre-built termose.duckdb may sit
# at the repo root (next to index.html) or under database/ for dev/tests — never
# commit or push it. Same for its write-ahead log.
*.duckdb
*.duckdb.wal
# Never commit parquet files (source terminologies, usage-count samples, etc.).
*.parquet

